2.8.0.name: drupal/planyo

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

2.8.0.description: This module embeds the Planyo.com online reservation system. It is intented for Drupal v7 or later. Before using it, you'll need to create an account at planyo.com. Please see http://www.planyo.com/drupal-reservation-system for more info.
